# u-boot env on the Superbird's eMMC.
#
# Stock Amlogic MPT puts the env partition at user-area offset
# 0x07400000 (116 MB). The u-boot binary uses CONFIG_ENV_SIZE = 64KB
# (a 4-byte CRC + ASCII env vars, padded to 0x10000), so fw_setenv
# only touches that first 64KB even though the partition itself is
# 8MB.
#
# Format: <device>  <offset>  <env_size>
/dev/mmcblk0  0x07400000  0x10000
